OL,6,FIn a letter to Lisa Nandy MP, the
OL,7,FCulture, Media and Sport Secretary, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "We believe Bury is the perfect
OL,9,Flocation for the new football
OL,10,Fregulator.
OL,12,F"As with so many of our great English
OL,13,Ftowns, football is woven into the
OL,14,Ffabric of Bury. Across the borough we
OL,15,Frepresent four non-league clubs Bury
OL,16,FFC, Radcliffe FC, Ramsbottom United
OL,17,Fand Prestwich Heys.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
