OL,3,CNew football regulator must 'be based
OL,4,Cwhere sport is woven into fabric'
OL,6,FThe bill is back in the House of
OL,7,FCommons after it cleared the House of
OL,8,FLords in March on its journey to
OL,9,Fbecoming law.
OL,11,FChanges made by the Government to the
OL,12,FBill, in response to concerns raised
OL,13,Fin the Lords, included placing a duty
OL,14,Fon the regulator to avoid having a
OL,15,Fnegative impact on the financial
OL,16,Fgrowth of English football as well as
OL,17,Finvestment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
