OL,3,CNew football regulator must 'be based
OL,4,Cwhere sport is woven into fabric'
OL,6,FKogan, who has previously advised the
OL,7,FPremier League and the EFL on
OL,8,Ftelevision rights deals in a 45-year
OL,9,Fcareer as a media executive, business
OL,10,Fleader and corporate advisor, is now
OL,11,Fset to head up the watchdog intended
OL,12,Fto ensure football clubs in the top
OL,13,Ffive tiers are financially sustainable.
OL,15,FThe regulator is also crucially set to
OL,16,Fhave 'backstop' powers to impose a
OL,17,Ffinancial settlement between the
OL,18,Fleagues if they cannot agree one.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
